  "description": "<p>Surface Pro、联想ThinkPad Helix、东芝Kirabook、戴尔XPS 12等一批高端Windows 8机器都有同一个让人讨厌的地方：那就是他们的高分辨率显示屏都太清晰绚丽，使得用户界面经常变得非常的小。文字也因此而变得难以阅读和难以进行相关的触 摸操控。<strong>但这种情况很快就会得到改变，Windows 8.1正式Retina高清分辨率显示屏支持，让用户在越来越多的高品质设备上缩放用户界面，获得更好的使用体验。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2dedde42/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242824.htm&amp;t=Windows+8.1%E4%B8%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%83%8F%E7%B4%A0%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%B1%8F%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242824.htm&amp;t=Windows+8.1%E4%B8%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%83%8F%E7%B4%A0%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%B1%8F%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242824.htm&amp;t=Windows+8.1%E4%B8%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%83%8F%E7%B4%A0%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%B1%8F%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242824.htm&amp;t=Windows+8.1%E4%B8%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%83%8F%E7%B4%A0%E5%AF%86%E5%BA%A6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%B1%8F%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E8%A7%86%E7%BD%91%E8%86%9C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googlepl